Package ca.phon.phonexg4

Class PhonexBaseVisitor<T>

java.lang.Object
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.AbstractParseTreeVisitor<T>
ca.phon.phonexg4.PhonexBaseVisitor<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The return type of the visit operation. Use Void for operations with no return type.
All Implemented Interfaces:
PhonexVisitor<T>, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeVisitor<T>
public class PhonexBaseVisitor<T>
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.AbstractParseTreeVisitor<T>
implements PhonexVisitor<T>
This class provides an empty implementation of PhonexVisitor, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
